reviewText: Not what you expect. No techniques shown and no tips that you don't already know. I could teach the "instructor" a thing or two myself. Save your money and watch a hundred similar people on YouTube. Also it ends up being a musical at the end.
Not what I expected.. No techniques shown. But ends up being a musical.
